OL,5,G2215 Long Lost Family Special: The
OL,6,G     Spanish Baby Scandal
OL,7,     FThe team meet with two women who
OL,8,     Fbelieve babies from their families
OL,9,     Fwere stolen at birth during the
OL,10,     Fhistoric scandal in Spain that
OL,11,     Ftook place from the 1930s into the
OL,12,     Fearly 1990s. Ruth, whose first
OL,13,     Fchild was born in Spain in 1992,
OL,14,     Ftells Davina McCall and Nicky
OL,15,     FCampbell that she believed her
OL,16,     Fdaughter had died at birth but
OL,17,     Fsuspicions have come to light in
OL,18,     Frecent years that she may have
OL,19,     Fbeen stolen instead. Maria Elena
OL,20,     Fcomes to the team for help on
OL,21,     Fbehalf of her 93-year-old mother,
OL,22,     FAna, who believes her twin babies
